<tr id="L7"><td><a href="#L7">7</a></td><td>ODO:  Commander, there are still elements opposed to the peace treaty between Cardassia and Bajor on both sides. We have to be prepared for trouble.</td></tr>

<tr id="L8"><td><a href="#L8">8</a></td><td>SISKO:  I realise that. But while the Cardassians are here, I want the Bajorans to get used to seeing them walking on the Promenade, buying from their shops, eating from their restaurants, getting to know them as something other than brutal overseers.</td></tr>

<tr id="L9"><td><a href="#L9">9</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: Dax enters</td></tr>

