<tr><td></td><td>LOCATION--Wardroom</td></tr>
<tr id="L96"><td><a href="#L96">96</a></td><td>SISKO:  The signalling platform we've designed is intended to be positioned in the Gamma Quadrant at this point, two kilometres from the far mouth of the wormhole.</td></tr>

