<tr id="L129"><td><a href="#L129">129</a></td><td>SISKO:  I don't have an agenda, Odo. I want this project to succeed because I want the peace treaty to succeed. If I thought for a moment there was any possibility that this communications relay could cause damage to the wormhole, I'd put a stop to it right now.</td></tr>

<tr id="L130"><td><a href="#L130">130</a></td><td>ODO:  That's not the agenda I was referring to, Commander.</td></tr>

